{
  "stem": "26022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was such a brilliant grade school student that I was told to skip the last year.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was always among the youngest one when I went to high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tell us about your schooling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- well, by then-- when I was about 10, which would be '23-- by then, of course, things had settled down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had gotten in a position where he could afford to send me to a private school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a school which had originally been founded by a very forward and progressive-looking parents to give girls a chance to pursue an academic career, which meant at age 10, it was decided, you are going to go to the university.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if you want to go to public schools, that's another story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if you want to enter this type of what was called gymnasium, which has nothing to do with gymnasium, or realschule, which was more science-oriented, then you were destined, hopefully, to become a professional.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, girls in those days were only given free spots in boys' schools.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If there were two vacancies, two girls could come in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Next year, another family moved into the area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was only one, one vacancy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So one girl had to stay home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was before my generation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that is why this school and two or three others were established to give girls an uninterrupted academic schooling.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I got into a realgymnasium, combined science with languages, a combination of realschule and gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- Would you tell us the name of the school and how you might spell it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Madchen-- ?] Girls' Realgymnasium, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Albertgasse-- ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Madchen ?] Realgymnasium Acht.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the 8th district.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
